{\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname country-region}}United States{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} is any judge, these two camps are unlikely to sit back and navel-gaze. Semi-failed 
states typically disintegrate. A bloodied (perhaps even nuclear) second civil war is in the cards.
\par Should the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname country-region}}United States{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
