ary ideology of the neo-conservatives. Spreading values, such as democracy, should better be left to }{\field\fldedit{\*\fldinst {\rtlch \af0 \ltrch \f0  HYPERLINK "http://samvak.tripod.com/ngos.html" }}{\fldrslt {\rtlch \af0 \ltrch \cs20\f0\ul\cf2 NGOs}
