ns of existence through the practice of ideology. It smoothes over contradictions and offers false (though seemingly true) solutions to real problems. Thus, ideology has a realistic attribute - and a dimension of representations (myths, concepts, ideas, i
mages). There is harsh, conflicting reality - and the way that we represent it both to ourselves and to others. 
\par }{\rtlch \ab\ai\af0\afs24 \ltrch \b\i\f0\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid5012951\charrsid5012951 "This applies to both dominant and subordinate groups and classes; ideologies do not just convince oppressed groups and classes that all is well
