The Problematic determines which issues, questions and answer
s are part of the narrative - and which are overlooked. It is a structure of theory (ideology), a framework and the repertoire of discourses which - ultimately - yield a text or a practice. All the rest is excluded. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid5012951 {\rtlch \af0\afs24 \ltrch \f0\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid5012951 \page }{\rtlch \af0\afs24 
\ltrch \f0\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid5012951\charrsid5012951 It is, therefore, clear that what is omitted is of no less importance than what is included in a text, or a practice. What the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname country-region}}United States{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} declines or neglects to incorporate in the resolutions of the Security Council, in its own statements, in the debate with its allies and, ultimately, in 
its decisions and actions, teaches us about {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname country-region}}America{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 and its motives, its worldview and cultural-social milieu, its past and present, its mentality and its practices. We learn from its omissions as much as we do from its commissions. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid5012951 {\rtlch \af0\afs24 \ltrch \f0\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid5012951\charrsid5012951 
The problematic of a t
ext reveals its historical context ("moment") by incorporating both inclusions and omissions, presences and absences, the overt and the hidden, the carefully included and the deliberately excluded. The problematic of the text generates answers to posed qu
estions - and "defective" answers to excluded ones. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid5012951 {\rtlch \af0\afs24 \ltrch \f0\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid5012951\charrsid5012951 
